00:12:09,447 --> 00:12:10,713
-Have you a wish ready?

272
00:12:10,813 --> 00:12:12,513
-Who, me?

273
00:12:12,613 --> 00:12:14,780
[giggles]

274
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:18,280
Actually, I'm just happy to
be spending the day with you.

275
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,380
-Truly?

276
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:22,180
If so, then allow me
to make it a reality.

277
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:26,113
Ugh!

278
00:12:26,213 --> 00:12:27,580
-Oh no you don't!

279
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:30,713
-Uh, jeez, he almost wasted it!

280
00:12:30,813 --> 00:12:32,913
-Well, all right then, my dear.

281
00:12:33,013 --> 00:12:34,380
Race me to that hilltop.

282
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,880
[laughing]

283
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:38,380
-Wait up, silly!

284
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,347
-Ha, ha.

285
00:12:39,447 --> 00:12:40,347
Slowpoke!

286
00:12:40,447 --> 00:12:40,888
Ha, ha.

287
00:12:42,413 --> 00:12:43,347
