289
00:12:46,613 --> 00:12:48,180
I twisted my ankle!

290
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:48,747
[gasp]

291
00:12:48,847 --> 00:12:50,013
-Pigtailed girl!

292
00:12:50,113 --> 00:12:51,480
-It hurts.

293
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,947
