294
00:12:54,047 --> 00:12:54,913
-Ow, ow.

295
00:12:55,013 --> 00:12:56,413
Ow.

296
00:12:56,513 --> 00:12:57,213
-Oh.

297
00:12:57,313 --> 00:12:59,013
-Now I've got you.

298
00:12:59,113 --> 00:12:59,913
