Aw.

475
00:20:04,813 --> 00:20:06,580
Why so cold, my love?

476
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,847
-Um, Ranma.

477
00:20:14,947 --> 00:20:15,847
-Stay back!

478
00:20:17,447 --> 00:20:18,747
Leave me alone.

479
00:20:18,847 --> 00:20:19,847
I couldn't do it.

480
00:20:21,147 --> 00:20:21,880
It's over.

481
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:24,080
All of it, it's over!

482
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:24,621
-Ranma!

483
00:20:25,847 --> 00:20:26,713
-Wait.

484
00:20:26,813 --> 00:20:27,254
